headline.main: YIELDING OF PARIS IS URGED ON NAZIS; French Discuss Return of City to Retain as Part of Price of Full Collaboration VICHY STILL NEGOTIATES German Request for More War Help and Care of Wounded From Russia Reported

lead_paragraph: VICHY, France, Oct. 9 -- Although Marshal Henri Philippe PeStain, Chief of State, and Admiral Francois Darlan, the Vice Premier, are away from Vichy for at least another twenty-four hours, it is no secret that certain diplomatic exchanges are occurring in their absence.
abstract: J de Lacretelle quoted on collaboration problems; return of Paris to Petain as part of collaboration price discussed
